---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Support — Mirage Atlas"
  description="How to reach us, how to report a bug, and how we handle feedback."
  canonical="https://mirageatlas.com/support"
>
  <main class="container-page py-20">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-ink-400 hover:text-white">&larr; Home</a>
    <h1 class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Support</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-ink-300">
      One inbox, staffed by the person who built the app. No ticket number, no escalation queue, no automated first response.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="mailto:support@mirageatlas.com" class="card block p-6 hover:border-atlas-500/50">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Email support</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
          For bug reports, crash logs, feature requests, pricing questions, or press enquiries.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-sm text-atlas-200">support@mirageatlas.com</p>
      </a>

      <a href="mailto:privacy@mirageatlas.com" class="card block p-6 hover:border-atlas-500/50">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Privacy requests</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
          Data-access or deletion requests under UK GDPR. We respond within 30 days.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-sm text-atlas-200">privacy@mirageatlas.com</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-16 max-w-2xl space-y-6 text-ink-200">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">When reporting a bug</h2>
      <p>The more of this you can include, the faster we can fix:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>Device model and OS version (e.g. iPhone 15 Pro, iOS 18.3).</li>
        <li>App version (Settings &rarr; About).</li>
        <li>Which game pack you were using.</li>
        <li>The exact question you asked, if you're comfortable sharing it.</li>
        <li>What you expected vs. what happened.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Response times</h2>
      <p>Weekdays: typically within 24 hours. Weekends: 48–72 hours. We reply to every genuine message; we do not run an auto-responder.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
